<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samasta bhava <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>ya śrī prithvīvallabha <unclear>ma</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>rājādhirāja paramēsvara <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>bhaṭṭāraka satyāśraya kuḷa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>cāḷukyābharaṇa śrī mattrai <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>lladēvara rājyamuttarōttarābhivṛddhi (pra)
<lb n="7" break="no"/>(va)rdhamānamācaṁdrārkka tāraṁbaraṁ salu(ttami)
<lb n="8" break="no"/>re tatpāda padmōpajīvigaḷappa sama <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>(ta) pañca mahāsabda mahāmaṇḍaḷēsvaraṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>tī puravarādhīśvaraṁ mūvaḍigaṇḍa ripumaṇḍaḷika <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/>ya rāyakaṭaka munniṟiva kārttavīryya kuḷatiḷa <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/>di samasta praśasti sahitaṁ śrīmanmahāmaṇḍa <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="13"/>carasareḍadoṟeyichcāsira manāḷuttamire (mā) <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="14"/>kavattanā<unclear>ḍa</unclear> taṁtrapāḷa gaṁgara cāvuṇḍamayyaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="15"/>ṇada nelavīḍinōḷ binnapaṁ geydu paḍeya svastyanēka <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="16"/>ga saṁghāta vīcichāyalavaṇābdhi paḷeya vaḷeya (paḍeṁ) <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="17"/>ga pāriyātra tanmadhye dēsādhipati <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="18"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vanatyugra narasira <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

